2.title: Hottest Summer Albums
2.plot: The warmer months ahead will bring new summer soundtracks for pool parties and BBQs. The StyleList gets the dish on the most anticipated albums for summer playlists.

3.title: Summer Shoes
3.plot: The StyleList gets the dish on the must-have summer shoes every girl should have stocked in her closet this season.

4.title: Summer Menswear
4.plot: Summer brings back traditional colors, modern shapes and classic pieces. From 50's inspired shirts to distressed denim, The StyleList countdown helps with navigating the latest menswear trends for summer wardrobes.

5.title: Summer Hair Trends
5.plot: Summer hair is all about feeling light and natural, with no major upkeep. The StyleList rounds up the top five hair trends this summer.

6.title: Rio 2016 Olympics Travel Must-Sees
6.plot: Headed to Brazil to catch the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro? From its sexy beaches and iconic sights, The StyleList shares its top picks for travel must-sees in Rio.

7.title: Travel Essentials
7.plot: When you're ready to hit the road this summer whether you're travelling to Yellowstone, Vegas or the sandy beaches of Miami, make sure you're prepared with the right travel essentials. The StyleList gets the dish on the five must-haves for summer adventures.

8.title: Entertaining on a Budget
8.plot: Celebrate the warm weather by entertaining at home with The StyleList's guide to summer entertaining on a budget.

9.title: Black Owned Wineries
9.plot: In the U.S., there are over 8,000 wineries, however, less than 5% are owned by African-Americans. Although the numbers are small, African-American winemakers are steadily increasing. The StyleList rounds up the best Black Owned Domestic Wineries.

10.title: How to Throw a Stylish Tailgate
10.plot: Football season is here. And to entertain your friends, you must know how to throw an epic football themed, tailgate that everyone will remember. For all you football fans; here's The StyleList's guide to celebrate this football season in style.

11.title: Must-Have Fall Shoe Trends
11.plot: Are you trying to step your shoe game up with the latest fashion trends? The StyleList reveals the top five most trending shoes for fall.

12.title: Must-Have Fall Accessories
12.plot: The StyleList has the latest trends in shoes, jewelry, furs, and handbags to take your fall wardrobe to the next level.

13.title: Fall TV Lineup
13.plot: The StyleList looks at the hottest must-watch Fall TV shows currently airing and one standout show.

14.title: Trending Pop Culture Halloween Costumes
14.plot: Learn how to dress like your favorite, fiercest singer or movie star to take your Halloween attire to the next level.

15.title: Men's Fall Fashion
15.plot: Men are now taking over the fashion scene this year and embracing these trends this season. The StyleList rounds up the hottest men's fall fashion trends.

16.title: Women's Fall Fashion Trends
16.plot: The StyleList rounds up the hottest women's fall fashion trends off the runways.

17.title: Throwing a Holiday Party
17.plot: Throwing a stylish holiday party, whether a sit-down dinner or a cocktail party, doesn't have to be stressful or cost a fortune. The StyleList shares a few tips for hosting holiday festivities without breaking a sweat.

18.title: Holiday Gift Guide for Her
18.plot: Are you having a hard time choosing the perfect gift for the special women in your life? The StyleList creates a list of amazing holiday gift ideas just for her.

19.title: Holiday Gift Guide for Him
19.plot: Some like to say that women are hard to shop for, but finding the right holiday gift for the men in your life can be equally challenging. The StyleList takes a little stress out of the equation with their roundup of the hottest holiday gifts for men.

20.title: Best Ski Resort Destinations
20.plot: Winter is upon us and it's that time of the year to pack the car for the first big ski trip of the season. It's not every mountain that's a perfect fit for the family, so The StyleList rounds up the top five best ski resort destinations that you'll absolutely love.

21.title: Top 5 People of 2016
21.plot: With the year coming to an end, there have been some pretty dynamic people who are worthy of acknowledgment in 2016. From sports to politics, The StyleList picks their top five people of 2016.

22.title: Top 5 Songs of 2016
22.plot: There's no doubt that 2016 was a year of amazing music. From summer anthems, chart-toppers and dance-worthy hits, The StyleList picks their top hits for best songs of 2016.

23.title: Top Moments of 2016
23.plot: Whether it was record-breaking movie deals or unforgettable performances, this has been a year to remember. The StyleList shares their top five moments of 2016.

1.title: New Years Eve 2016 Fashion Trends
1.plot: The best New Year's Eve outfits are the ones that don't hold back on glamour or sparkle. Whether you're gearing up for a girls' night or a big date with your boo, The StyleList rounds up the must-have New Years Eve fashions so you can ring in 2017 with style on the biggest party night of the year.

2.title: Award Season Red Carpet Trends
2.plot: The StyleList rounds up the top and hottest red carpet trends this award season and the details on the outfits of your favorite most fashionable celebrities.

3.title: Awards Season: Ones to Watch
3.plot: With so many veterans and break out stars on the rise this awards season, they're all worth keeping a close eye on. The StyleList rounds up their top five ones to watch in film this Awards Season.

4.title: Must-See Awards Season Movies
4.plot: Awards Season is upon us with a rich selection of amazing movies that went from Broadway revivals to the big screen, some based on true stories, and also beautiful coming of age tales. The StyleList rounds up their Top Five Must See Movies this Awards Season.

5.title: Valentine's Day Gift Guide
5.plot: Sometimes it's tough to wrap up an "I love you", and the challenge of picking out the perfect gift for Valentine's Day can be overwhelming. Instead of the classic chocolate and flower combo, choose the gift of an experience. From spa outings to wine tastings, champagne hot air balloon rides, fast cars and much more in-between, give a gift that's as timeless and treasured as the memories they create. The StyleList rounds up the best Valentine's Day gifts that goes far beyond a box.

6.title: New Orleans Travel Must-Sees
6.plot: Are you looking for southern hospitality with a Parisian vibe? How about creole and Cajun cuisine followed by dancing in the streets? If any of these sound good to you, then you may be overdue for a visit to New Orleans. Filled with tons of year-round events such as Essence Fest, Jazz Fest, and Mardi Gras and even this year's NBA All Star weekend. The StyleList rounds up their list of travel must-sees in New Orleans.

7.title: Award Season's Best Dressed
7.plot: The red carpet has seen an assortment of strong and unique fashion from the most stunning women in Hollywood. The StyleList rounds up those who made their best-dressed list this awards season.

8.title: Women's Spring Fashion Trends
8.plot: New York Fashion Week came and went but if you didn't blink, you probably caught it. As Fashion Week makes its way around the world The StyleList compiles a list of their favorites just to be sure you're caught up with the trends. Whether it's re-purposing closet staples or underwear becoming outerwear, you're bound to find something you love from the roundup of must-have women's spring fashion trends.

9.title: Budget Spring Break Travel Destinations
9.plot: Spring break is already here and for some travelers, that means seeking out beaches and sunshine, however spring break shouldn't break your bank. The StyleList rounds up the top five affordable spring break travel destinations.

10.title: Festival Season Fashion Must-Haves
10.plot: The excitement and thrill is real with the arrival of festival season. Looking the part is expected at crowd-pleasing must festivals like Coachella and Essence and choosing the right wardrobe is key. We've got you covered on what festival fashion should be packed in your bag. The StyleList rounds up festival season must-have trends.

11.title: Earth Day Eco-Friendly Fashion
11.plot: Earth day is here and there are so many ways to reduce your carbon footprint and decrease your addition to landfills that extend beyond planting trees and recycling plastic. While those methods are excellent, take it a step further all the way down to your closet. Curating a stylish environmentally-friendly wardrobe is the most chic way to celebrate Earth day and look fabulous while doing so. The StyleList rounds up fashion-inspired environmentally-friendly ideas to celebrate earth day, every day of the year.

12.title: Spring Beauty Trends
12.plot: It's officially spring and whether you braved the desert for Coachella or are travelling to New Orleans for Essence Festival, it's the perfect time to switch out your makeup routine for a few festival inspired looks. We caught up with our friends at RA Hair House, the new celebrity hair and makeup salon in West Hollywood, for the scoop on the hottest spring beauty trends adored by their celebrity clients.

13.title: Last-Minute Mother's Day Gift Guide
13.plot: Mother's Day rolls around every year, and every year we're overwhelmed with options. Moms can be the hardest to shop for, but we've made it easy with our roundup of last-minute Mother's Day gift ideas for the traveling mom, fashionista mom, and every mom in between.

1.title: Valentine's Day Spa Treatments
1.plot: This week on the StyleList, we kicked off the New Year with a high-energy workout with Jason Derulo, got our skate and grub on with Master Chef Derrick Fox and we are giving you the top three spa resort treatments to indulge in, just in time for Valentines Day.

2.title: Season of Her
2.plot: The StyleList catches up with Nike to get a sneak peek at the Jordan Brand's newest collection for HER, gets a taste of LA's best new restaurants and goes 'Black in the Day' in honor of Black History Month.

3.title: 2018 Oscar Viewing Party
3.plot: The StyleList catches up with some of the best golfers in the world at the 2018 Genesis Open, gets a sneak peek of the LA Times Food Bowl and and closes out Awards Season with an Oscars Viewing Party at the Orlando Hotel in Los Angles.

4.title: iHeartRadio, Nicky Hilton, Rachel Zoe + Bumble Hive
4.plot: The StyleList catches up with music's biggest superstars at the I Heart Radio Music Awards, get a sneak peek of Nicky Hilton's 'mommy and me' capsule collection, and have a day of empowerment and style with Rachel Zoe at the Bumble Hive in Los Angeles.

5.title: Garden Party, Guadeloupe, & Derby Day
5.plot: The StyleList kicks off spring by hosting a Style and Society Garden Party with celebrity friends and favorite brands, travels to Guadeloupe for a taste of the French-Caribbean, and celebrates race day fashion at the Santa Anita Derby.

6.title: Celebrating Pride with Laverne Cox
6.plot: The Beverly Center and The Advocate came together to kick-off PRIDE month and celebrate the LGBTQ community at their Champions of PRIDE event hosted by Laverne Cox at Beverly Center's Farmhouse. The event honored LGBTQ advocates and allies who have made a significant impact on their community over this past year. Guests enjoyed live performances and photo moments at the one-of-a-kind mural created by Lovewall artist J. Goldcrown.

7.title: Nickelodeon Kids Choice Sports
7.plot: Chloe Kim, Stephen Curry, Serena Williams, Russell Wilson, Kevin Durant, Venus Williams, Lindsey Vonn, Shaun White, host Chris Paul, and more took home coveted orange blimps at Nickelodeon's Kids' Choice Sports 2018, the only show that celebrates the intersection of kids' culture with their favorite athletes. The slime-filled celebration was hosted by Houston Rockets' point guard and former NBA All-Star MVP Chris Paul.

imdb.title: The StyleList
plot: _The StyleList_ (qv) covers the latest fashions, trends, and pop culture in a fast paced and entertaining format. An on-camera extension of Style and Society magazine. Hosted by Kinya Claiborne.::ONX Media Group
